review_text: Hey, devs ! I honestly enjoy this game very much . There are so many modes, that freaking detailed analysis and so much more about this . But there is a major issue . This game rewards experience and matches played over raw speed . Like I personally got a 30+ score and my rating is sub 1200 . Meanwhile there are people with 2500+ ratings but sub 20 scores in individual matches . I believe the game should reward skill more than raw experience as it will make the experience feel more rewarding .
